Pro-Putin TV anchor Vladimir Solovyov said on Russian controlled state TV that the UK had got "totally boorish" and suggested the idea of using the 16,000 mph nuke on it. The RS-28 Sarmat can fly more than 11,000 miles and carry 15 warheads. It could completely obliterate the UK in one strike. Mr Solovyov told his viewers: "As it turned out, one Sarmat means minus one Great Britain." FOLLOW BELOW FOR LIVE UPDATES... 